---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import principalImg from '../assets/principal_photo.png';
import signatureImg from '../assets/signature.jpeg';
---

<section id="PrincipalSection"class="pt-0 pb-8 md:pb-16 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="w-full h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 via-amber-500 to-blue-900 shadow-lg relative z-20"></div>

  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-amber-50/50 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-50/50 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/3 -translate-x-1/3 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02] pointer-events-none" 
       style="background-image: radial-gradient(#172554 0.5px, transparent 0.5px); background-size: 20px 20px;">
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-2 md:px-4 relative z-10 mt-6 md:mt-10">
    
    <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-3 md:gap-10">
      
      <div class="w-[40%] md:w-[42%] relative group shrink-0">
        
        <div class="absolute -inset-1.5 md:-inset-3 border md:border-2 border-amber-500/30 rounded-tl-[20px] rounded-br-[20px] md:rounded-tl-[30px] md:rounded-br-[30px] z-0 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:rotate-1"></div>
        <div class="absolute -inset-1.5 md:-inset-3 border md:border-2 border-blue-900/10 rounded-tr-[20px] rounded-bl-[20px] md:rounded-tr-[30px] md:rounded-bl-[30px] z-0 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:-rotate-1"></div>

        <div class="relative rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-b-2 md:border-b-8 border-amber-500 z-10 bg-slate-200">
             <Image 
               src={principalImg} 
               alt="Principal of LKEA" 
               widths={[300, 600, 800]}
               sizes="(max-width: 768px) 300px, 600px"
               quality={75}
               loading="lazy"
               class="w-full h-full object-cover shadow-lg rounded-2xl"
             />
             
             <div class="absolute top-2 left-2 md:top-4 md:left-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-300 via-amber-500 to-amber-700 text-white w-9 h-9 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-lg border-2 border-white/30 animate-pulse-slow z-20">
                <span class="text-[9px] md:text-xl font-black leading-none drop-shadow-md">35+</span>
                <span class="text-[4px] md:text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter md:tracking-wide">Years Exp.</span>
             </div>

             <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full bg-gradient-to-t from-blue-950/95 to-transparent pt-8 pb-2 px-2 md:pt-10 md:pb-5 md:px-5">
                <p class="text-[8px] md:text-xs font-bold text-amber-400 tracking-widest uppercase mb-0.5">Director</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-white leading-tight">Mr. Bishnudeo Kumar</p>
             </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-[60%] md:w-[58%] relative flex flex-col justify-center">
         
         <div class="mb-1 md:mb-4">
            <span class="inline-block bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 text-blue-900 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-[10px] md:text-[12px] px-2 py-0.5 md:px-3 md:py-1 rounded-full">
               Principal's message:
            </span>
         </div>
         
         <h2 class="text-sm md:text-4xl font-heading font-black text-blue-950 leading-tight mb-2 md:mb-4">
            A Legacy of <br>
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-amber-800">Educational Excellence</span>
         </h2>

         <blockquote class="border-l-2 md:border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-2 md:pl-5 italic text-slate-700 text-[9px] md:text-lg mb-2 md:mb-5 bg-slate-50 py-1 md:py-3 rounded-r-lg pr-1 md:pr-4 leading-tight md:leading-relaxed shadow-sm">
            “True education builds strong character, disciplined habits, and confident minds — not just academic results.”
         </blockquote>

         <div class="space-y-1 md:space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-[8px] md:text-base leading-snug md:leading-relaxed text-justify font-medium">
            <p>
               "Welcome to <strong>Lord Krishna Educational Academy</strong>. For over <span class="text-amber-700 font-bold">35 years</span>, I have dedicated my life to education believing that the foundation built in early years shapes a child’s entire future.
            </p>
            <p class="hidden md:block">
               At our school, education goes beyond textbooks. We focus on discipline, moral values, personal attention, and a safe learning environment, ensuring every child grows with confidence and clarity from Nursery to Class 8.<strong> I personally assure every parent that your child’s safety, character development, and academic growth are our top priorities"<strong>
            </p>
            <p class="md:hidden">
               At our school, education goes beyond textbooks. We focus on discipline, moral values, personal attention, and a safe learning environment, ensuring every child grows with confidence and clarity from Nursery to Class 8.<strong> I personally assure every parent that your child’s safety, character development, and academic growth are our top priorities"<strong>
            </p>
         </div>

         <div class="space-y-1 md:space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-[8px] md:text-base leading-snug md:leading-relaxed text-justify font-medium">
            <p>
               
            </p>

            <p>
               It gives me immense satisfaction to share that many of our former students, who built their early foundation with us, are today serving the nation and society as doctors, engineers, educators, and professionals across diverse fields".
            </p>
            <p class="hidden md:block">
            
            </p>
            
            <p class="md:hidden">
               
            </p>
         </div>

         <div class="mt-2 md:mt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-end gap-1 md:gap-4">
             <div class="relative">
                 <Image src={signatureImg} alt="Signature" class="h-6 md:h-14 w-auto opacity-90" />
                 <div class="h-px w-full bg-slate-300 mt-1"></div>
             </div>
             
             <div class="text-[7px] md:text-xs font-bold text-blue-900 uppercase tracking-wider">
                Director & Principal
             </div>
         </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    @keyframes pulse-slow {
        0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
        50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
    }
    .animate-pulse-slow {
        animation: pulse-slow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
  </style>
</section>